data.description: Nestled in the heart of Hominy, just minutes from the serene Skiatook Lake and Hominy Lake, This idyllic property updated in 2022, boasts all the comforts of home, from a fully fenced yard to exquisite hardwood floors and butcher block countertops. This charming home offers 2 cozy bedrooms, ideal for restful nights and peaceful mornings. The kitchen includes a stainless refrigerator and gas stove for your culinary needs. The stylishly appointed bathroom ensures that your daily routine is both comfortable and convenient. The fully fenced yard provides a secure haven for pets, children, and gardening enthusiasts alike. Imagine the possibilities for creating your own outdoor oasis, whether it's hosting BBQs, gardening, or simply enjoying a sunny afternoon. Conveniently located across the street from the Elementary School. Take advantage of the unique opportunity this property offers - it qualifies for a USDA No Money Down Loan, making homeownership more accessible than ever.
